E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Hey if Tony gave you my number, then it's okay bro.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~嘿，既然Tony给了你我的电话，那就没有问题，兄弟。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Ray, hey man, I hate to disappoint you.
~z~Sometimes I dream about being a rich playboy who everyone loves.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~有时我会幻想自己是个人见人爱的花心公子哥。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Now I do something and it ain't good enough because I ain't hanging out around the neighborhood with them.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~现在我做了什么了，你又嫌弃我没跟他们混在一起。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Yusuf. You staying out of trouble, man?
~z~They aren't as bright as you and you have disrespected them. Laughed at them with your rich friends
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~他们没你那么有活力。你还对他们不尊重，和阔佬朋友一起嘲笑他们。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~and I know it takes a lot to put up with you and keep you on the path.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~我还知道跟你长期相处、让你不误入歧途很难。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Nice man? Mami, he's a loan shark! You didn't borrow no money did you?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~大好人？老妈，他放高利贷的！你没问他借钱吧？

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Luis. Hello, my friend. Did you like the car. Did you like the other gift?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~Luis。你好啊，朋友。喜欢这辆车吗？喜欢车上的小礼物吗？

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~This is not an opportunity you want to miss out on,
~z~You better believe it, bro. Totally guilt free. It's business, business, business with me.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~你一定要相信我，兄弟。完全无罪。我一直在工作、工作、工作。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Listen, I thought you should know that things is cool with Tony now. It looks like we might be okay.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~听着，现在Tony这边没事了，我跟你说一声。应该不会有事了。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Shit. If he even half liked pussy, you know how many bitches he'd fuck?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~妈的，但凡他对女人有点兴趣，你知道他会日多少逼吗？

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~You can respect him from a college library, not just the bandstand of his nightclub.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~你可以在大学的图书馆尊重他，而不是夜店的舞台上。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Heh heh, yeah. Kibbutz on a motherfucking kibbutz, huh! Yeah but I've taken this shit over.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~没错。Kibbutz现在在基布兹*，哈！但这里已经归我管了。~n~(以色列的集体主义社区)

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~My wayward son, I hope you ain't brought no curses on the family.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~我任性的儿子，希望你没有给家族招来诅咒。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Yeah I don't know where you heard that...
~z~Anyway, it changes. Give him a break, for me okay?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~总之，经常变的。别逼他太紧，看在我的面子上。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~No. He helped me with my shopping. He is a real gentleman.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~没。买东西的时候他帮了我。他真是个绅士。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~It's just usually you start throwing stuff at me and telling me I'm wasting my life.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~只是每次你都会朝我扔东西，说我在浪费人生。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Look, I just wanted to apologize to you. I was an asshole.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~听着，我想跟你道个歉。之前是我不对。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~You are though to the M. Kibbutz Holding Company, Tanya's away from her desk.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~感谢联系M. Kibbutz控股公司，Tanya现在不在。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~especially as I hear that "Gay" Tony Prince's ship is sinking.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~听说「基佬」Tony Prince的船就要沉了吧。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~It's right on the Middle Park, prime location, one of the most exclusive in the city.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~就在中心公园，黄金地段，自由城最高档的地段之一。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~And you haven't got any time for your old friends.
~z~Give him some slack. He's Tony fucking Prince! He's a legend
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~放宽心吧。他可是Tony Prince！传奇人物！

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~But listen, can you come and meet me at the construction site? I have something to discuss.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~但是听着，你能来建筑工地找我吗？我有事和你商量。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~I love those guys, Mami. I do what I can to help them.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~我对他们有感情的，老妈。我会尽力帮助他们的。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~No, man, they a long way from good.
~z~Yeah, why's that make me think you're about to ask me to do some dumb shit?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~是吗，我怎么觉得你又要找我搞什么事情了。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Hey, hey, Iike, hey do some fucking work. Huh?
~z~Hey, those conversations are usually Tony's department.
~z~Yeah, okay, man, I'll try to come by.
~z~Stay away from him, Mami. Listen to me on this.
~z~Yeah. Thanks for the sensible advice. I'll try. See you soon, okay.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~好。多谢你的建议，我试试吧。再见啦。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~No, Mami, it ain't like that at all. You wanted me to do something.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~不，老妈，不是这样的。之前你想让我做些什么，

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~This is not like thing in your American supermarket. It has sell by date.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~这可不是你们美国超市的商品。是有保质期的。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Shit, man, I already killed for it. I'm thinking, alright?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~妈的，伙计，我已经杀红眼了。我在考虑，好吗？

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Luis, why do you never come to see your mama?
~z~Hey, this ain't going, man, and there's nothing you can do. Me and Tony got to find some way to dig ourselves out.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~嘿，这不现实，哥们。你也帮不了我们什么。我和Tony只能靠自己找条出路。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Don't you "Yo" me. You think I'm one of your little nightclub putas?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~别跟我「哟」。你当我是夜店里的婊子吗？

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Just come to my house, we will talk.
~z~You wish to accept. Of course. No one refuses Ray Bulgarin.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~你会选择接受，意料之中。没人能拒绝Ray Bulgarin。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Yeah, not good, bro. Sometimes it's hard with that guy.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~不太好，兄弟。他有时候也很艰难。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~No, I did. There is a little bit of fun for you in the glove compartment. I think you will enjoy it.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~不，有必要。我在车的储物柜里给你准备了小惊喜，你会喜欢的。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Was. Now it's more of a umm, how do I say this - dictatorship you know. Hah ha.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~之前是。现在更像是...怎么说呢，独裁制度。哈哈。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Hello, Shalom. This is Mori. I'm getting spiritual with nature and shit in the Promised Land.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~你好，贵安。我是Mori，正在应许之地修炼自然之道。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Bandstand? Huh, Dios Mio. Look, I can't ever win with you. I love you, Mami.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~舞台？我的天哪。行吧，说不过你。我爱你，老妈。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Thanks a lot, bro. You didn't need to do that though.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~多谢了，兄弟。没必要这么客气的。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Ay Dios mio, Mami. I'll come by soon.
~z~ I am spending some time here while I catch up with some old friends
~z~I brought some real modern world shit into this joint. It's a much better use of my time.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~我给这里带来了现代社会，这样才对得起我宝贵的时间。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~That's cute, man. I might be in touch.
~z~No, could you say it again, please?
~z~It's a special machine, but what you have done for me recently is more special.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~这是辆特别的车，但你之前为我做的事，更加特别。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~What you doing with that man? Why don't you go to college like a good boy.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~你跟他在一起干嘛？为什么不能做个上大学的好孩子？

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~For Armando, for Henrique. Old friends are the best friends, Luis.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~见Armando，见Henrique。老朋友才是最好的朋友，Luis。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Alright, man. I'll check that out. Yo, and thank you again.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~好的，哥们。我会去看看的。哟，多谢了。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Hijo. I need you to come home. There is a little complication.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~儿子，你快回家一趟吧。情况有点复杂。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~I'm still not getting it, what about a third time?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~我还是没听懂，要么再说一次？

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Great! Come hang out at my apartment.
~z~Shit, I think the signal's dropping, man. Later, bro.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~妈的，好像信号不太好，伙计。回见，兄弟。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~I did not take you for the sensitive type.
~z~ Don't speak back to me, son.
~z~The Mafia? I've had problems with some union fucks on the site. Sometimes that shit just goes away.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~黑手党？我的工地之前也被傻逼工会占领过。有时候他们自己就散了。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Mami, I didn't mean anything like that. I'm stressed at the moment. Tony's putting me through hell.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~老妈，我没有那个意思。我现在压力很大，都是Tony害的。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Solid gold! Only the best for you, Luis. It makes a statement, doesn't it?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~纯金打造！只为你准备最好的。倍儿有面子，对吧？

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~bad boy and lover, so leave me a fucking message.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~兼坏小子兼情人，有事就留言吧。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~We are brothers. It is nothing. I've got three more myself. See you soon, my friend.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~我们是兄弟，不算什么。我自己还有三把呢。再见了，朋友。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Not that great. My father, he is a very passionate and angry and very disrespectful man.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~不太好。我父亲是一个很敏感、很暴躁、很无礼的人。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Shit, it sure does. Thanks a lot, Yusuf.
~z~Oh yeah. You're the Russian who was asking about coke, hookers, and corpses. Yeah, I'm sorry we couldn't accommodate.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~哦对，你就是那个咨询毒品、妓女、杀手的俄国人。恕我们没有这些服务。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Cash ain't going to fix this problem, okay. We got a crazy Russian after us and we in some deep shit with some Cosa Nostra morons.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~靠钱解决不了我的问题，好吧。我们被一个俄国疯子追杀，还跟几个科萨诺斯特拉蠢蛋有矛盾。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~and I need help with some things.
~z~This is Ray Bulgarin Liberty City phone. I call you back.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~这是Ray Bulgarin在自由城的号码。我会联系你的。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Come to my house and we will discuss it.
~z~I'm okay. Busy, you know. Shit's hectic. Tony's in trouble.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~还行吧。就是有点忙，事情很多。Tony遇到麻烦了。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Please leave a brief message and it may be returned.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~在你留言之后我可能会回拨答复。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~We need people, so pack your bags and come out here. That material shit, it don't matter anymore.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~我们很缺人手，背上行李加入我们吧。物质之类的，不必为此烦恼。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~You could learn so much from him.
~z~ I come to this city, I want to be the straight Tony Prince. That's my fucking dream, motherfucker.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~我来自由城，就是为了当直男版Tony Prince的。这就是我的梦想，妈个逼的。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~I've been out tilling the land and it really put shit in perspective for me, you know?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~最近一直在种地，让我有了不同的想法。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Don't be too proud, Luis. You ever need something, you call Yusuf, okay? See you round, bro.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~别太自信了，Luis。需要什么了就联系Yusuf，好吗？再见了，兄弟。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Yo you putting me in an awkward position, man. I can't tell you this thing's taken care of - 'cause it's not.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~我现在就很尴尬，伙计。我不能说事情已经处理好了，因为真没办好。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~You and your faggot boss will be killed for this. I will do everything in my power to...
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~你和你的基佬主子都要为此丧命。我会尽我所能...

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~And now I am going to fuck with you, you little cunt.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~现在轮到我搞死你了，小贱逼。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~This could be your chance to achieve something without the Princess Tony.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~把握住这个机会，没有基佬Tony你也可以成事。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Treat him with respect, you hear me, son. Look after those who have looked after you.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~对他放尊重点，听见了吗，儿子。不要忘记照顾过你的人的恩情。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~What do you take me for? I'm a giver, not a taker. I don't need anything from you.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~你把我当什么了？我是给予者，不是索取者。我不需要你帮我了。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Yusuf don't like his main dude unhappy.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~Yusuf不想让他的好哥们愁眉苦脸。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~There are others in this city who would kill for opportunity.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~自由城有的是人愿意为这个机会杀红眼。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~No. Not at all. That's how things seem, but trust me, that wasn't my intention.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~不不不，哪有的事。看起来是这样，但相信我，我不是那个意思。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Alright. I'll be by sometime. Just don't wait up.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~好的，我有空就来。你别一直等我。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Hah, you don't need to sacrifice no frogs for me.
~z~Hey I don't even know what it is yet.
~z~Pathetic. Why did I have faith in this loser?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~太可悲了，我怎么会相信这个失败者？

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~I don't care if you're 78. You wanna eat? Work. Oh uh, sorry, Lou. Yeah, now where were we?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~78岁又怎么样？想吃饭吗？干活。哦呃，抱歉，Lou。聊到哪了来着？

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~I am told you are the man to talk to.
~z~Sometimes, man. Sometimes I dream about working in Burger Shot.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~我有想过，老兄。有时，我也会幻想自己在汉堡店工作。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Then maybe you should have asked! Instead you run around this city making a fool of me.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~不知道你不会问吗！结果你当我是白痴，到处乱跑。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Please leave a message and we will get back to you.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~有事请留言，之后我们会进行答复。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Mami, I thought you wanted me to respect him.
~z~We met at your club. I am Ray Bulgarin.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~我们在店里见过的。我是Ray Bulgarin。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~These people were fucking backwards. Sharing and shit? Come on, I mean, what, communism?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~这群人太落后了。分享互助？我去，这啥啊？共产主义吗？

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Listen, man, I got a real busy schedule.
~z~I wanted to make a gift of my car to you.
~z~I know you, hijo, and I know your bog ego
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~我了解你的，儿子，还知道你很自大。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Mr. Tony, for all his faults, has been just about able to do that.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~Tony先生，虽然他也有错，但他做到了这些。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Unfortunately, I'm busy being a rich, successful and very popular international superhero,
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~很不幸，我忙着当有钱、成功而且备受欢迎的国际大英雄，

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Mr. Tony gave me your number, there are some other matters I need to discuss before we get down to the real shit.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~Tony先生给了我你的电话，干正事之前我还有些别的事要找你聊。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Luis. I saw that nice man Mr. Santo again.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~Luis，我又遇到那个大好人Santo先生了。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~The guy who wants to talk about franchising your clubs.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~就那个想加盟你们家夜店的人。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Hey, Mr. Bulgarin. About this offer, man.
~z~Listen, man, I told you. I didn't know shit about who owned them diamonds.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~听着，伙计，我都说了。我压根就不知道钻石是谁的。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Yeah, Tony's kept me on a path alright. I don't know if it's the right one though. I love you, Mami.
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~是，Tony没让我误入歧途，但有没有走上正途就不知道了。我爱你，老妈。

E2MF1AU.original: ~z~Yeah, we were saying good bye, Mori.
~z~Well how much you need? How much money you want me to throw at this problem for you?
E2MF1AU.translated: ~z~需要几个子？需要我掏多少钱帮你解决问题？
